# Claude Code / impeccable — personal permissions and ephemeral runtime state, not shared project
# config. .claude/skills/, PRODUCT.md, DESIGN.md, .impeccable/design.json, .impeccable/live/,
# and .impeccable/critique/ ARE tracked — this only excludes the local-only files.
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.impeccable/hook.cache.json
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.playwright-mcp/
